Ni '''Ferdinand Pascual Aguilar''' (a.k.a. ''Ka Freddie Aguilar'', ''Lolo Freddie'' odin '''Freddie Aquilar'''; inianak Pebrero 3, [[1953]] ed [[Ilagan, Isabela]]), kankanta ya musikano dia [[Filipinas]]. Too ya galing so bilay dia pang-rendisiyon ed "[[Bayan Ko]]"  ed kanta para oposisiyon ran rehimo ken [[Ferdinand Marcos|Marcos]] migay nia ed 1986 [[People Power Revolution]].

